Nollywood actress, Nnanji Charity has revealed how she escaped the request for sex for the role by movie producers and directors. The pretty light-skinned actress said her journey to Nollywood was quite rough because sex for the role was the order of the day. She, however, revealed how she was able to avoid such requests.   Seun Kuti & Egypt 80 band partner Roland corporation     BON unveils logo for The Nigerian broadcasting Award     Toyin Abraham, Odunlade rejoice as Bamidele Onalaja…   “My journey into Nollywood has not been easy why because sex for the role is the order of the day, once you are not ready to submit your body to either producer or director then you have no movie roles,” said Nnanji. On how she made her way to become a rising star without offering sex, she said: “I was able to avoid those things because  I was capable of producing my movie.” Also speaking on the selection of movie roles, Nnanji said she would never act in a bedroom scene no matter how much money is involved.